00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:50.600
Toda mi propiedad

00:04:50.800 --> 00:04:52.319
y los 60 millones de Xintong

00:04:52.319 --> 00:04:53.360
que recibí de Chi Shan.

00:04:53.959 --> 00:04:55.120
